  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "1.     Provide support to construct 71 Bio-gas Toilets2.     Construct and Install 1300 Bio-sand Water Filters3.     Drinking Water Supply: build 2 new reservoir and construct 21 new tap stands for the community people in Ipilbasti village, Rautahat and Jhurjhure, Makawanpur 4.     School BSF Construction in 2 schools.5.     Construction of 15 Ring Well and install one Hand Pump in each ring well. 6.     Provide Agriculture and Animal Husbandry Training and Refresher Training.7.     Organize Natural farming study tour.8.     Provide support for Model Animal Husbandry9.     Provide seed money to start the saving in the group10.  Provide seedling to 110 households under Agro-forestry.11.  Provide Agricultural tools to encourage natural farming.12.  Conduct Follow - up meeting with farmers group and provide13.  Provide seed money to farmers' groups to improve their saving habits under micro-credit initiative.14.  Provide Health, Hygiene and Sanitation Training15.  Provide 3 days training on Nutrition and refresher training16.  Provide Safer Motherhood Training.17.  Provide Menstrual Hygiene Management Training.18.  Run Adult Functional Literacy Classes19.  Run Post Literacy ClassesCarry out Leadership Training to enhance the capacities of the local leaders"
    },
    "ne": null
  },
